SECURITIES INDUSTRY (SCR)
</IN>
<LP>
   NEW YORK -- The New York Stock Exchange said a seat was
sold for $320,000, down $5,000 from the previous sale Aug.
14. Seats are currently quoted at $310,000 bid, and $330,000
asked.
