   IMPERIAL CHEMICAL INDUSTRIES PLC (London) -- Philip
Daubeney, 51-year-old managing director of ICI India, was
named regional executive of this chemical company's African
and Eastern region, effective in October, succeeding Roy
Allen, 55, who is to retire. George Ewart, 52, general
