     Manufacturers .............. 370.53   372.38   366.49
     Retailers .................. 235.13   234.81   231.00
     Wholesalers ................ 191.64   193.20   185.15
                                                                                                       

   Total business sales ......... 544.43   538.95   520.51
                                                                                                       

   Inventory/sales ratio ........   1.46     1.49     1.50
</TEXT>
