however. The bankruptcy court has already given final
approval to Allegheny's reorganization under a new name,
Sunbeam/Oster Corp. And the prospective owners, Japonica
Partners, indicated yesterday that they plan to work toward a
resolution giving it control of the consumer products
company.
   Directors expect to install new top management, led by
Chairman Paul B. Kazarian, once ownership is officially
transferred to Japonica.
